channel.title: INDIR3CT - Downtown (Lofi)
channel.description:
Hey everyone! Been really excited to get this track finished. Recently I've been getting into the same old repetitive routine, and have really been lacking in creativity.
I really went all out on this one, and tried to create something different, something unique, something me.
As always _ any comments, likes, reposts, feedback, and support is appreciated.
https://soundcloud.com/indir3ct/downtown Thanks so much for sticking with me and supporting me to this point, and I hope this track isn't too trashy to listen to haha [spoiler]If you are wondering... this **is** track 5 of an upcoming Debut album.[/spoiler] Love, INDIR3CT
